Package org.livingdoc.repositories.file

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DocumentFile
    A DocumentFile wraps a File that contains a class Document
    FileRepository
    A FileRepository is a interface DocumentRepository in a locally mounted filesystem.
    FileRepositoryConfig
    FileRepositoryConfig contains the configuration for a class FileRepository.
    FileRepositoryFactory
    A FileRepositoryFactory is a interface DocumentRepositoryFactory used to create class FileRepository instances with a specific class FileRepositoryConfig.
    FileResolver
    Class to handle resolving file for the class FileRepository.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    FileDocumentNotFoundException
    FileDocumentNotFoundException is thrown when a class Document could not be found within a class FileRepository.
